message: Hi Bob, I'm excited to offer you this great product. I think you'll really like it. I'm willing to sell it to you for $110.
Thanks for the offer, Alice! I'm interested but $110 is a bit higher than I was hoping for.  Would you be willing to do $95?
I appreciate your interest in the product, Bob. I can do $105, but I'm not sure I can go any lower than that.
